replies.body:
This new way of getting BE is very, very slow. Please bring back the ways of earning some after games as not only will levels become harder to earn but getting two cheap champions in one capsule and only earning around 200 BE off a level is not very fun at all. It feels like we will have to start paying RP at higher levels for new champions with the lack of BE. I just beg that you bring back BE after every game. Please.
RIP mastery levels and champions...
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}
